OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780503064
OL,3,CFarmer sentenced after dead animals
OL,4,Cfound scattered through fields
OL,6,FA farmer has been handed a suspended
OL,7,Fprison sentence after inspectors found
OL,8,Fdead animals scattered through his
OL,9,Ffields and farm buildings.
OL,11,FDavid Coulson, 61, of Sand Lane,
OL,12,FMarket Rasen, pleaded guilty to ten
OL,13,Fanimal welfare offences including
OL,14,Fcausing unnecessary suffering to
OL,15,Fanimals and breaching strict legal
OL,16,Frequirements on the disposal of
OL,17,Fdeadstock.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
