FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780503064
OL,3,CFarmer sentenced after dead animals
OL,4,Cfound scattered through fields
OL,6,FIt followed a number of inspections at
OL,7,Fhis farm between July 2022 and January
OL,8,F2024, by Trading Standards and the
OL,9,FAnimal and Plant Health Agency.
OL,11,FIn 2022, animal remains were found
OL,12,Facross the farm, including decomposing
OL,13,Fcarcasses, bones and skulls.
OL,15,FSeveral animals were also found in so
OL,16,Fmuch distress that they needed to be
OL,17,Fput down to prevent further suffering.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
