OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780503064
OL,3,CFarmer sentenced after dead animals
OL,4,Cfound scattered through fields
OL,6,FThe investigation also found that
OL,7,Fattempts had been made to conceal
OL,8,Fcarcasses during official inspections,
OL,9,Fand that misleading information had
OL,10,Fbeen provided to enforcement officers.
OL,12,FCoulson was handed a 13 month prison
OL,13,Fsentence, suspended for two years, and
OL,14,Fordered to pay costs of over #39.000.
OL,16,FHe was also banned from owning,
OL,17,Fkeeping, dealing, transporting or
OL,18,Fbeing involved in the keeping of
OL,19,Flivestock indefinitely.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
