OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1780503064
OL,3,CFarmer sentenced after dead animals
OL,4,Cfound scattered through fields
OL,6,FEmma Milligan, Operational Delivery
OL,7,FManager for Lincolnshire Trading
OL,8,FStandards, said: "It would have been
OL,9,Fimmediately clear to anyone visiting
OL,10,FDavid Coulson's farm with our officers
OL,11,Fthat animals were being kept in
OL,12,Fextremely poor conditions.
OL,14,F"Coulson's role transporting animals
OL,15,Fmeant that large numbers of them came
OL,16,Funder his care, and many were exposed
OL,17,Fto neglect despite repeated advice and
OL,18,Fsupport from Trading Standards and the
OL,19,FAnimal and Plant Health Agency to
OL,20,Fimprove standards.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
